extendedInfo.description: MyCareer.com.auâs free Android app allows you to find jobs wherever you might be. â¨So you can now put your next move in the palm of your hand.What can the app do for you?â¢ Search and review thousands of jobs on MyCareer.com.auâ¢ Save your CV to MyCareer.com.au and apply for jobs straight from your Android handsetâ¢ Plus, our app helps you manage your job search process by allowing you to:â¢ Sort and shortlist jobs you are interested inâ¢ Add personal notes and comments to jobsâ¢ Email potential jobs straight to your inboxâ¢ Sync the app with your MyCareer account Feedback and suggestionsTo provide feedback and/or suggestions on the MyCareer.com.au Android app, please email promotions@mycareer.com.au

reviews.title: Pretty decent
reviews.comment: Decent app to check out what are out there in the real market. Same experience with the website minus all the ads is what u will see.
reviews.author: Hoang Hai Nguyen

reviews.title: Reasonable App, Poor Service
reviews.comment: The actual application is quite well designed and appears to work reasonably well, though it be great to see the ability to upload a resume directly from the host smartphone or tablet, in addition to optional notifications. The biggest let-down however, seems to be the actual service - new job listings are few and far between, whilst certain (MyCareer) competitors not only have at least quadruple the number of listings, but also more regular updates.
reviews.author: Gregory Opera
